dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows the Gulf of Messenia and surrounding region during the military campaigns of Venetian general Francesco Morosini during the Morean War (1684-1699). Text below map: Nachdem der Venetianische General Capitain Morosini die Vestung Coron erobert ...
